Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不象话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然出入这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房间里竟还有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画 漫画 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么低俗而愚蠢的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑犬（hellhound）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻把春香给我找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂家的长女竟然沾染上这种愚劣的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.67,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,390)}{\fad(1000,1000)}[…最喜欢了！]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兴趣被父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家里 父亲正等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边还放着我房间里藏着的周边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间被搜过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季漫展上买的东西被他拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠地摔在地板上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么辛苦才买到的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还做了其它很多过分的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不肯听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来带我回去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在父亲改变心意前 是不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是叶月小姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只要这是春香小姐的意愿 我就会遵从于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能让春香小姐独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我伴随您的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春香小姐的随侍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像事情还挺麻烦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠子 由香里老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就住在我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回家又无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我家父母都在海外 所以有房间空出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说可以让她们住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 裕君 面红耳赤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨 笨蛋 我什么都没想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 给你们添麻烦的话 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给我们添麻烦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全 绝对 一丁点也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反而让我觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕君 你还真是大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是 不纯异性交往还是不行~的~哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁 谁会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕君 脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不象话 你在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吵死了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 春香和女仆入住绫濑家的庆祝会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠子小姐好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒也很会喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要成为秘书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒也一定要会喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此平日的训练也是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个很努力的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那么高尚的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想变成像她那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(200,200)}我是女强人 那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(200,200)}那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人先生 这个火锅是裕人先生做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是用手边的材料随便做了下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合做入赘女婿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 别贴上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事情想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于春香的事~情~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 一五一十地招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候关系这么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我和春香并不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称呼直接就是「春香」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和春香只是同班同学而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然关系特殊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话就爽快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为春香小姐的女仆有知情的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝不是一般所说的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互凝视着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下流 你这个色男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么样 怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是同居了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样升级做我姐夫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说要做爸爸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那边情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲他果然在夏季漫展的会场里安排了密探
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的直属部队——黑犬（hellhound）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直译的话就是地狱的看门狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23个小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天就会有援军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超强力的无敌的最终兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能有所期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是初夜 对姐姐要温柔些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:07:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女 色 魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}{\fad(200,200)}日文是耳年增 指"理论"性知识丰富的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 春香小姐的事可以拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去她会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以请你带她去卧室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要在这附近巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐的护卫也是作为女仆的我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里与宅邸不同 安全保障上有不安因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不像那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这次我真的去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人的脸这么近…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…公主抱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对面就是春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 可以打扰下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 房间里很黑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是晚上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽 虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不止是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以说房间非常暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很黑的地方独自一人不会觉很寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这样觉得吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你害怕一个人睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 在家里有玩偶陪我一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐她们也会巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不觉得害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以说我能不能一起睡在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我本不想添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请 请 请让我睡在你旁边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是innocent smile的创刊号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走的时候只带了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书对我来说是很特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我非常 非常重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能睡得着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能牵着你的手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 不行的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要牵手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不论遇到什么事都是春香的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭马上就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏 怎么了 这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了 姐姐的位置被父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人先生 外面被追兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被 被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没人响应 我就擅自进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 把春香还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就砍过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把别人家的门 弄坏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁无礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有按过门铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我按住她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 你这家伙 让开 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事情我已经不介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一时的迷失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 不可能会被那种东西给吸引住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别像小孩子一样耍脾气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回听话的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有觉得自己不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲你完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜欢那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢迟钝娘小秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢熬夜恶魔小皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢夜想曲女子学院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我最喜欢innocent smile
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝不是一时的迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会认可的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画 漫画 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能执着于那种东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这混蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这混蛋诱骗了春香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的兴趣有那么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样低劣的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与乃木坂家的长女完全不符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么能这么肯定？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对春香的兴趣知道些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香为什么会喜欢上这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是以什么样心情在喜欢着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香对她的兴趣投入的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与别人对兴趣投入的感情是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热心于此 拚命努力 认真投入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底里喜欢着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么 只有秋叶原系不能被认可？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像赶上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是来阻止父亲的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么无聊的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子让到一边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该让开的应该是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看形势也很不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也有好好地努力学习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的一点兴趣也可以认可吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 多管闲事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在意她也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 如您所说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实也是明白的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 还有裕人所说的话是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画 漫画之类的 我虽然不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是春香自己的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她第一次自己决定做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只有相信她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那种事 你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 父亲好像也认可了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜诉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能干啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得有认可你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊扰到你们了 真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后为了让你的兴趣得到认可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学业修养方面也要好好地努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 添了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说多少是有些头脑发热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是做了没有大人样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也说得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今也和很多人接触过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一个能这样正面对我说出自己的意见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这样事情就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里 你还在睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:34.60,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,360)}{\fad(800,0)}『…大~哥哥☆』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐邀请了裕人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是难得的约会里 椎菜姐姐却出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆亲密接触 骚乱不断
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 乃木坂春香的秘密 大~哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直击~你的心脏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:56.00,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正到关键时刻 别来打扰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:11.58,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指尖相触的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:13.31,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 啐?啐?啐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.90,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌鬼登场了 耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:21.18,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.68,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.35,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必传说中的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:34.74,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是晕红了双颊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:40.09,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心下有意口难开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:45.58,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜」字开头的那个词
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:51.51,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要恋爱 就得主动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:56.92,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花雪月 唱啊跳啊 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.13,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知所谓！？ 这就是LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.71,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双唇一颤…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.39,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的是「秘密?」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.59,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出食指 贴上嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:11.27,edch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密模式 悄悄地说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:56.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だいじなトコで　ねえジャマをしないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:11.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まさに　手と手が触れた瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:13.31,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら　ちっ?ちっ?ちっ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オジャマ虫やってくる　イエイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:21.18,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなり絶妙です　タイミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぐずぐず　してはいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわさのあの娘も　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:34.74,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ピンキィーに　頬っぺた染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:40.09,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言いたくて　でも言えない　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:45.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,てっぺんに「ス」の付く言葉です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:51.51,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コイをしたいなら　よっといで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:56.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花しょって　夢しょって　歌いましょう　らんらんらん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ワケワカンナイ！？　そりゃLOVEなんですもん
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,クチビルが動いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.39,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも　ここからは“ヒミチュ?”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人さしゆび　ゆびっ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:11.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ナイショ?モード　ひそひそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:18.48,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要半遮半掩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.71,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望你夺去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.97,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是命运 一秒也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.28,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想梦见新生的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.42,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬紧双唇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.72,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪随疼痛而高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.83,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无奈 无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:41.95,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 这就是爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.01,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！ 做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.26,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.39,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰触那柔软的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.48,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦涩褪尽之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.17,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦喷薄而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:58.18,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:02.18,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双目含情 视线交错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.47,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.77,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Bitter Tune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:16.09,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不分开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:18.48,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半分ならあげない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.71,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべて奪って欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.97,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命なら1秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.28,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれ変わる夢を見た\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.42,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,クチビルを噛んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.72,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛いほど高ぶっちゃうね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.83,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもしょうがない 戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:41.95,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ… これが愛なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.01,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do！しよう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.26,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるえる ふるえる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.39,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな核心に触れてよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.48,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひどい苦さの後で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.17,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほとばしる甘い夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:58.18,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ホラ つながる つながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:02.18,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡みつく視線で つかまえて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.47,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「わたしのこと大好きですか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.77,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おねがい Bitter Tune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:16.09,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離さないで…
